Question: The right image shows a beagle that is airborne with a blue sky featured predominately in the background

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the dog a beagle?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the dog airborne?')

ANSWER3=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER1} and {ANSWER2}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER3)
```
